base"><span class=3D"strut" style=3D"height: 0.6444em;"></span><span class=
=3D"mord">4</span></span></span></span></span>).</p>
<p>Die neue Subnetzmaske lautet <code>255.255.255.192</code> oder <code>/26=
</code>. In bin=C3=A4rer Schreibweise:</p>
<p><code>11111111.11111111.11111111.11000000</code></p>
<p><img src=3D"https://app.ausbildung-in-der-it.de/storage/eVlqkJvz82n76GwQ=
qhAb29sPE1ljwmILSJjRefc1.svg" alt=3D""></p>
